👗 StyleVerse — Final Notes

«DreamVerse → Mega Mini Game #2
Final Name: StyleVerse ✅»

---

🎯 Purpose

StyleVerse is DreamVerse's complete Fashion, Beauty, Creativity & Lifestyle Mega Mini Game.

Players can design their own fashion, create brands, participate in fashion shows, unlock secret collections, and express their creativity.

It is designed for both boys and girls.

---

🎨 Main Features

👕 Outfit Designer

Players can create and customize:

- T-Shirts
- Shirts
- Hoodies
- Jackets
- Pants
- Dresses
- Suits
- Traditional Clothes
- Costumes
- Shoes
- Bags
- Crowns
- Backpacks
- Wings
- Accessories

Everything can be customized.

---

💄 Beauty Studio

Players can customize:

- Makeup
- Hairstyles
- Nail Art
- Glasses
- Jewelry
- Hats
- Watches
- Accessories

---

🎨 Advanced Design Editor

Players can edit:

- Colors
- Materials
- Patterns
- Stickers
- Logos
- Layers
- Decorations

Every design is completely original.

---

🤖 AI Design Studio

Players can upload their own original image.

AI converts it into a wearable 3D item.

Examples:

- Teddy → Backpack
- Butterfly → Wings
- Flower → Hair Clip

Rule

AI only converts original or user-created designs.

No copyrighted brands, logos, or characters.

---

🏢 Fashion Brand System

Players can create their own brand.

Customize:

- Brand Name
- Brand Logo
- Brand Theme
- Brand Description
- Brand Color

Players can publish their own clothing collections.

---

🏆 Fashion Shows

Regular fashion competitions.

Examples:

- Spring
- Royal
- Beach
- Halloween
- Christmas
- Space
- Future
- Cute

Players may:

- Participate
- Skip

Winners receive titles and recognition.

---

📸 Photo Studio

Players can:

- Take Photos
- Select Poses
- Choose Backgrounds
- Create Posters
- Save Albums

---

🎁 Unlock System

No clothing is purchased with coins.

Items are unlocked by:

- Exploration
- Challenges
- Hidden Locations
- NPC Quests
- Secret Puzzles

---

🌍 Country Collections

Special fashion collections from different countries.

Examples:

- India
- Japan
- Korea
- France
- Brazil
- United Kingdom
- China

---

🎉 Seasonal Collections

Limited seasonal outfits.

Examples:

